{"title":"Hexo & Inside","date":"2022-10-16T16:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Oct 17, 2022","L":"10/17/2022","MM-DD":"10-17"},"link":"2022/10/17/hexo-&-inside","tags":["Hexo","blog","github","theme"],"updated":"2022-10-17T16:00:00.000Z","content":"<h3 id=\"pre-requirement\">pre-requirement<a title=\"#pre-requirement\" href=\"#pre-requirement\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>node.js &gt;= 8.10, recommand &gt;=10.0</li>\n<li>npm</li>\n<li>git</li>\n</ul>\n<p>for more detail, please visit: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-tw/docs/\" target=\"_blank\">https://hexo.io/zh-tw/docs/</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"setup\">setup<a title=\"#setup\" href=\"#setup\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"install-theme---inside\">install theme - <code>Inside</code><a title=\"#install-theme---inside\" href=\"#install-theme---inside\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ npm i hexo-theme-inside</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>for more detail, please visit: <a href=\"https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"quick-qtart\">quick qtart<a title=\"#quick-qtart\" href=\"#quick-qtart\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"modify-the-global-_config.yml\">modify the global <code>_config.yml</code><a title=\"#modify-the-global-_config.yml\" href=\"#modify-the-global-_config.yml\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">theme: inside</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"theme-configuration\">theme configuration<a title=\"#theme-configuration\" href=\"#theme-configuration\"></a></h4>\n<ol>\n<li>create a config file named <code>_config.inside.yml</code></li>\n<li>Copy <a href=\"https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside/blob/master/_config.yml\" target=\"_blank\">theme config yml</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>for more detail, please visit: <a href=\"https://blog.oniuo.com/theme-inside\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.oniuo.com/theme-inside</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"setup-for-github-action\">setup for github action<a title=\"#setup-for-github-action\" href=\"#setup-for-github-action\"></a></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>create a new repo named ‘<code>username</code>.github.io’ where username is your account name of github</li>\n<li>install dependency <figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ npm i hexo-deployer-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>modify the section <code>deploy</code> inside <code>_config.yml</code>, be sure to modify the <code>username</code><br>\nfor more detail, please visit: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-tw/docs/github-pages.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://hexo.io/zh-tw/docs/github-pages.html</a> <figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># Deployment</span><br><span class=\"line\">## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment</span><br><span class=\"line\">deploy:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  type: &#x27;git&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  repo: &#x27;https://github.com/username/username.github.io&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  branch: &#x27;main&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"usage\">usage<a title=\"#usage\" href=\"#usage\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo cl</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo g</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo s</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo d</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo g -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","prev":{"title":"RIPv2 & RIPng Introduction","link":"2022/10/17/ripv2-ripng"},"next":{"title":"A step by step how to start docker-compose container at boot","link":"2022/05/13/step-by-step-start-docker-compose-container-at-boot"},"plink":"https://jason19970210.github.io/2022/10/17/hexo-&-inside/","toc":[{"id":"pre-requirement","title":"pre-requirement","index":"1"},{"id":"setup","title":"setup","index":"2"},{"id":"install-theme---inside","title":"install theme - Inside","index":"3"},{"id":"quick-qtart","title":"quick qtart","index":"4"},{"id":"setup-for-github-action","title":"setup for github action","index":"5"},{"id":"usage","title":"usage","index":"6"}],"reading_time":"191 words in 1 min"}